        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Founded in 1978 by Mr. Ghassan Abi<br/>Yaghi & Sons, ATCO S.A.L. is a renowned family-owned business celebrated<br/>for its quality products and exceptional service. Starting with the widely<br/>recognized \"SOFTEX\" brand in Lebanon and the Gulf region, ATCO S.A.L.<br/>has expanded its product offerings and market reach over the years.</p><p><strong>Company History</strong></p><p>ATCO S.A.L., a family-owned business<br/>founded in 1978 by Mr. Ghassan Abi Yaghi & Sons, entered a new era in 2024<br/>with a significant leadership transition. Bassam Abi Yaghi, son of the founder<br/>and a recognized expert with over 25 years of experience in the home linens<br/>industry, assumed full ownership and management, acquiring all shares. Mr. Abi<br/>Yaghi brings a dynamic vision to the company, with a strong commitment to<br/>advancing its operations, solidifying its position as the leading provider in<br/>the home business sector across Lebanon and the region, and achieving the<br/>highest international standards. He aims to achieve this through strategic<br/>initiatives focused on innovation, enhanced customer experience, expansion of<br/>product offerings, and adherence to global best practices. This transition<br/>builds on the strong foundation laid by the previous generation, while<br/>positioning ATCO S.A.L. for continued growth and success under experienced and<br/>globally-minded leadership.</p><p><strong>Our Services</strong></p><p>ATCO S.A.L. provides comprehensive<br/>home and hospitality solutions, catering to retailers, boutiques, hypermarkets,<br/>and multinational hotels across Lebanon and the Gulf countries. Leveraging<br/>cutting-edge market intelligence, we offer tailored services to meet diverse<br/>client needs. Our expertise extends to custom embroidery services, allowing for<br/>personalized products with logos, intricate designs, and lacework. We also<br/>offer client branding, producing products under client brand names and logos,<br/>and manufacture for major brands, adhering to their high standards.</p><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>Our Brands</strong></p><p>We offer a portfolio of high-quality,<br/>trusted product collections, including:</p><p>Softex</p><p>L'oreiller Gold</p><p>Elite Home Fashion</p><p>Daynasty</p><p><strong>Export Markets</strong></p><p>ATCO S.A.L. proudly exports its<br/>Softex brand products to Canada, Europe, and the GCC, demonstrating a<br/>commitment to quality and excellence on a global scale.</p><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>Our Network & Partners</strong></p><p>We maintain strong partnerships with<br/>reputable companies and factories specializing in premium woodworks, kitchens,<br/>and furniture, enabling us to meet the diverse needs of our market.</p><p></p><p><strong>B2B and Retail</strong></p><p>ATCO S.A.L. serves both the B2B and<br/>retail markets, offering high-quality products through various channels,<br/>including direct sales, retail stores, and online platforms.</p><p><strong>Home Linens Expertise</strong></p><p>We specialize in the production of<br/>home linens, providing an extensive range of products designed for comfort and<br/>luxury, including:</p><p>Bed Sets</p><p>Comforters</p><p>Pillows</p><p>Mattress protectors &<br/>     Toppers</p><p>Kitchen linens</p><p>Bathroom linens</p><p>Blankets</p><p><strong>Our Mission</strong></p><p>To be the leading supplier<br/>     of linen products to the corporate landscape in Lebanon and the<br/>     surrounding region.</p><p>To utilize our market expertise<br/>     to provide superior solutions and recommendations during our clients'<br/>     decision-making processes.</p><p>To offer high-quality<br/>     products at competitive prices through our extensive market access and<br/>     resources.</p><p><strong>Our Vision</strong></p><p>To become a pioneering force in the<br/>home and hospitality solutions industry, setting benchmarks for quality,<br/>service, and innovation across the region.</p><p><strong>Our Values</strong></p><p>Quality: We are committed to delivering products of the highest quality,<br/>     ensuring complete customer satisfaction.</p><p>Integrity: We operate with transparency, honesty, and respect in all our<br/>     interactions.</p><p>Innovation: We continuously seek to innovate and improve our offerings to meet<br/>     the evolving needs of our clients.</p><p>Customer Focus: Our clients are at the heart of everything we<br/>     do, and we strive to exceed their expectations.</p><p><strong>Our Team</strong></p><p>Our dedicated team of market specialists<br/>understands the unique needs of our clients. By leveraging our industry<br/>expertise and multi-disciplinary skills, we ensure our clients receive<br/>consistently high standards of service.</p><p><strong>Product Excellence</strong></p><p>Our products are meticulously crafted<br/>to meet the highest standards of quality and durability. Our range includes<br/>banquet linens, table linens, bed linens, bath linens, curtains and draperies,<br/>and light sanitary products.</p><p><strong>Market Reach</strong></p><p>Our products have gained widespread<br/>recognition and trust in Lebanon and across the Gulf region. Our dedication to<br/>maintaining high standards has made SOFTEX a preferred choice for hotels, home,<br/>and restaurants.</p><p><strong>Innovation and Quality</strong></p><p>We continuously strive to improve our<br/>product offerings, incorporating the latest trends and technologies. Rigorous<br/>quality control processes ensure that every product delivers on our promise of<br/>excellence.</p><p><strong>Customer Satisfaction</strong></p><p>Customer satisfaction is our top<br/>priority. We are committed to understanding and exceeding client expectations,<br/>providing personalized solutions and exceptional service.</p><p><strong>Sustainability</strong></p><p>We are mindful of our environmental<br/>impact and dedicated to sustainable practices. our products are designed with<br/>sustainability in mind, using eco-friendly materials and processes wherever<br/>possible.</p><p> </p>",
            "text_size": "typeset",
